♪ The fireball that we rode
was moving ♪

01:44.720 --> 01:48.361
♪ But now we got
a new machine ♪

01:48.520 --> 01:51.205
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

01:51.360 --> 01:55.160
