We close in 10 minutes.

02:05.640 --> 02:07.051
I'm well aware.

02:07.200 --> 02:08.201
Set me down a Moscow Mule

02:08.360 --> 02:11.728
and two of whatever
the lady's having.

02:17.880 --> 02:19.882
It's rosewood.

02:20.040 --> 02:22.327
Hand-carved by Italian artisans.

02:22.480 --> 02:24.084
You know
how people always say

02:24.240 --> 02:26.720
you shouldn't put your hand
in front of a speeding train?

02:26.880 --> 02:28.882
<i>I guess.</i>

02:29.080 --> 02:30.081
Well, what those people
don't know

02:30.240 --> 02:32.925
is that sometimes
there's an eight-year-old boy

02:33.080 --> 02:34.650
stuck on the tracks.

02:34.840 --> 02:36.410
You saved him.

02:36.560 --> 02:38.927
In a lot of ways,
he saved me.

02:39.080 --> 02:41.765
But, yeah, I saved him
from certain death

02:41.920 --> 02:43.922
30 years ago to this day.

02:44.080 --> 02:45.411
But, you know,
losing my clumsy old meathook

02:45.600 --> 02:47.284
wasn't too big of a price to pay.

02:47.440 --> 02:52.082
But I do like to honor it every year
by getting blackout drunk.

02:52.240 --> 02:53.446
♪ Let's go space truckin'... ♪

02:53.600 --> 02:55.329
Care to join me?

02:55.480 --> 02:56.766
(woman moaning )

02:56.920 --> 02:58.285
Ash:
Oh! Yeah!

02:58.440 --> 03:00.090
(woman moaning )

03:00.280 --> 03:01.520
♪ Space truckin'... ♪

03:01.680 --> 03:04.001
Yeah!
That sounds good!

03:04.200 --> 03:06.487
You like that, huh?
You like my wood?

03:06.640 --> 03:09.086
Oh! Please!

03:09.240 --> 03:11.129
I'm getting a little winded.

03:11.280 --> 03:13.601
Maybe we take a break
and focus on me for a bit.

03:13.760 --> 03:15.410
- Just a little more.
- Okay.

03:15.560 --> 03:16.561
<i>'</i> Yes!
_

