- ( grunting )
- Oh! Yes!

03:19.440 --> 03:22.284
I'm coming! I'm coming!

03:22.440 --> 03:24.169
We're coming for you.

03:24.320 --> 03:26.163
Jesus!

03:27.440 --> 03:29.283
What's wrong?
What happened?

03:29.440 --> 03:31.488
I was so close.

03:31.640 --> 03:34.120
Well, it's just, uh--
something happened

03:34.280 --> 03:37.409
that hasn't happened
in, like, 30 years.

03:37.560 --> 03:39.642
Ooh.
I got to jet.

03:39.800 --> 03:40.847
Really?

03:41.000 --> 03:43.651
Well, I could finish,

03:43.800 --> 03:46.201
but I got to be quick.

03:46.360 --> 03:48.328
Oh! Let's go!

03:48.480 --> 03:50.244
Yeah! There you go!

03:50.400 --> 03:53.006
- Yeah! Yeah.
- Oh, oh, yes!

03:53.160 --> 03:55.367
Oh: yes!

03:55.520 --> 03:57.249
(moaning )

